          <button class="hero-tab" onclick="switchHeroTab(2)"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3zM6 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM16 18v-3a5.972 5.972 0 00-.75-2.906A3.005 3.005 0 0119 15v3h-3zM4.75 12.094A5.973 5.973 0 004 15v3H1v-3a3 3 0 013.75-2.906z"/></svg>學員社群</button>
