  <section class="curriculum bg-cream fade-up" id="curriculum">
    <div style="max-width:var(--max-width);margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
      <div class="section-label">三大系統</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading">超級個體・人生系統</h2>
      <div class="divider" style="max-width:120px;margin:1rem auto;"></div>
      <p class="body-text" style="text-align:center;margin-top:1rem;">
        這套課程，整理了雷蒙從 0 到 1 的真實經驗，帶你正確地看懂時代的趨勢和局勢，打造一套經營自己或槓桿時間與資源的方法。從普通人，成為能聰明工作的「生活黑客」，再成為能打造理想生活的「超級個體」。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Venn Diagram (SVG) -->
    <div class="venn-wrap">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 560 500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <defs>
          <!-- Radial gradients for each circle -->
          <radialGradient id="gTime" cx="50%" cy="40%" r="50%">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#E77E47" stop-opacity="0.22"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#E77E47" stop-opacity="0.04"/>
          </radialGradient>
          <radialGradient id="gKnow" cx="40%" cy="50%" r="50%">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#21A4B1" stop-opacity="0.20"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#21A4B1" stop-opacity="0.04"/>
          </radialGradient>
          <radialGradient id="gInflu" cx="60%" cy="50%" r="50%">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#8B5CBA" stop-opacity="0.20"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#8B5CBA" stop-opacity="0.04"/>
          </radialGradient>
        </defs>

        <!-- Circles with mix-blend for natural overlap -->
        <g style="isolation: isolate;">
          <circle cx="280" cy="175" r="165" fill="url(#gTime)" stroke="rgba(231,126,71,0.15)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <circle cx="185" cy="330" r="165" fill="url(#gKnow)" stroke="rgba(33,164,177,0.12)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <circle cx="375" cy="330" r="165" fill="url(#gInflu)" stroke="rgba(139,92,186,0.12)" stroke-width="1"/>
        </g>

        <!-- 時間系統 -->
        <text x="280" y="115" text-anchor="middle" class="v-sub" fill="#b85a2a">找到熱愛的事</text>
        <text x="280" y="155" text-anchor="middle" class="v-title" fill="#374151">時間系統</text>

        <!-- 知識系統 -->
        <text x="145" y="340" text-anchor="middle" class="v-sub" fill="#18808a">強化擅長的事</text>
        <text x="145" y="380" text-anchor="middle" class="v-title" fill="#374151">知識系統</text>

        <!-- 影響力系統 -->
        <text x="415" y="340" text-anchor="middle" class="v-sub" fill="#6b3fa0">拓展商業價值</text>
        <text x="415" y="380" text-anchor="middle" class="v-title" fill="#374151">影響力系統</text>

        <!-- Intersection labels -->
        <text x="215" y="245" text-anchor="middle" class="v-label" fill="rgba(55,65,81,0.55)">閒職</text>
        <text x="345" y="245" text-anchor="middle" class="v-label" fill="rgba(55,65,81,0.55)">兼職</text>
        <text x="280" y="395" text-anchor="middle" class="v-label" fill="rgba(55,65,81,0.55)">正職</text>

        <!-- Center: 人生 -->
        <text x="280" y="305" text-anchor="middle" class="v-center" fill="#E77E47">人生</text>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <!-- Detail cards below Venn -->
    <div class="curriculum-details">
      <div class="curriculum-detail-card card-time" id="system-time">
        <div class="curriculum-num">系統 1</div>
        <div class="curriculum-title">時間系統</div>
        <div class="curriculum-desc">建立任務管理流程，用可持續的回顧機制，找到熱愛的事。學會正確使用行事曆和待辦清單、減少會議、推動專案的非同步溝通術。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="curriculum-detail-card card-knowledge" id="system-knowledge">
        <div class="curriculum-num">系統 2</div>
        <div class="curriculum-title">知識系統</div>
        <div class="curriculum-desc">活用 AI 和知識萃取流程，強化你所擅長的事，找到個人優勢和專業。學會怎麼有效閱讀、建立個人知識庫，讓每一次學習都能轉化為你的武器。</div>
      </div>
      <div class="curriculum-detail-card card-influence" id="system-influence">
        <div class="curriculum-num">系統 3</div>
        <div class="curriculum-title">影響力系統</div>
        <div class="curriculum-desc">不用離職創業，也能拓展你的價值，累積長尾的個人品牌。學會為什麼寫作是平凡人最好的投資、怎麼寫個人使用說明書、超級個體的商業模式。</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mid CTA -->
    <div class="mid-cta fade-up">
      <div style="width:160px;height:1px;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.15);margin:0 auto 2rem;"></div>
      <div class="mid-cta-heading">
        不只是線上課程，<br>而是一套<span class="typewriter-wrap"><span class="typewriter-text" id="typewriter-text"></span><span class="typewriter-cursor">|</span></span>
      </div>
      <p class="mid-cta-sub">從普通人，成為生活黑客，再成為超級個體。</p>
      <a href="<%= ctaLinks.joinCourse.url %>" class="cta-black"><%= ctaLinks.joinCourse.label %></a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================== -->
  <!-- SECTION 5: LEARNING      -->
  <!-- ======================== -->
  <section class="learning bg-dark fade-up">
    <div style="max-width:var(--max-width);margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="section-label">6 種學習模式</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="color:var(--cream);">打破傳統線上課的學習方式</h2>
      <div class="divider-light"></div>
      <p class="body-text-light" style="">
        為了讓每個人的學習成效更好，在《超級個體工作術》這堂課裡，準備了 6 種不同的學習模式，讓你可以依照自己的步調、學習偏好情境，自由切換、有效吸收。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="learning-layout">
      <div class="learning-modes">
        <div class="learning-mode active" data-mode="1" onmouseenter="setLearningMode(1)">
          <div class="learning-mode-num">Mode 01</div>
          <div class="learning-mode-title">完整文稿 ＆ 互動式講義</div>
          <div class="learning-mode-desc">每堂課加贈雷蒙精編的 Notion 講義，可線上互動註記，獲得更多補充資源；幫助你高效學習、反覆複習。</div>
        </div>
        <div class="learning-mode" data-mode="2" onmouseenter="setLearningMode(2)">
          <div class="learning-mode-num">Mode 02</div>
          <div class="learning-mode-title">雙機位高質感影片課</div>
          <div class="learning-mode-desc">採用雙機位拍攝＋精緻剪輯，畫面流暢有層次，就像你熟悉的專業精品課。</div>
        </div>
        <div class="learning-mode" data-mode="3" onmouseenter="setLearningMode(3)">
          <div class="learning-mode-num">Mode 03</div>
          <div class="learning-mode-title">全程實作教學</div>
          <div class="learning-mode-desc">教學工具類操作，全程螢幕錄影，清楚呈現每個步驟，就像我在你身旁帶著你一起。</div>
        </div>
        <div class="learning-mode" data-mode="4" onmouseenter="setLearningMode(4)">
          <div class="learning-mode-num">Mode 04</div>
          <div class="learning-mode-title">高效音頻課</div>
          <div class="learning-mode-desc">釋放你的雙手和設備，通勤或運動時也能輕鬆學習，善用碎片時間。</div>
        </div>
        <div class="learning-mode" data-mode="5" onmouseenter="setLearningMode(5)">
          <div class="learning-mode-num">Mode 05</div>
          <div class="learning-mode-title">視覺化知識圖卡</div>
          <div class="learning-mode-desc">複雜觀念一圖搞懂，幫助記憶與內化。</div>
        </div>
        <div class="learning-mode" data-mode="6" onmouseenter="setLearningMode(6)">
          <div class="learning-mode-num">Mode 06</div>
          <div class="learning-mode-title">課後作業 ＋ 學員社群</div>
          <div class="learning-mode-desc">每堂課設有作業練習、網狀學習的設計；不只寫自己的筆記，還能參考其他同學的觀點。</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="learning-preview">
        <div class="learning-preview-placeholder active" data-preview="1">Notion 互動式講義示意圖</div>
        <div class="learning-preview-placeholder" data-preview="2">雙機位影片課示意圖</div>
        <div class="learning-preview-placeholder" data-preview="3">螢幕錄影實作示意圖</div>
        <div class="learning-preview-placeholder" data-preview="4">音頻課示意圖</div>
        <div class="learning-preview-placeholder" data-preview="5">知識圖卡示意圖</div>
        <div class="learning-preview-placeholder" data-preview="6">課後作業社群示意圖</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:3rem;">
      <a href="<%= ctaLinks.joinCourse.url %>" class="cta-orange"><%= ctaLinks.joinCourse.label %></a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================== -->
  <!-- FEATURES + COURSE PREVIEW -->
  <!-- ======================== -->
  <section class="bg-dark fade-up" style="padding:3rem 1.5rem 4rem;">
    <div class="course-preview">
      <div style="max-width:var(--max-width);margin:0 auto 1.5rem;">
        <div class="section-label">免費試看</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading" style="color:var(--cream);">課程內容試看</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="course-preview-grid">
        <% coursePreview.filter(function(c) { return c.displayType === 'card'; }).forEach(function(c) { %>
        <a class="course-preview-card" href="<%= c.videoUrl %>">
          <div class="course-preview-thumb">
            <img src="<%= c.thumbnail %>" alt="">
            <div class="course-preview-play"><div class="course-preview-play-btn"></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="course-preview-info">
            <div class="course-preview-num"><%= c.unit %></div>
            <div class="course-preview-title"><%= c.title %></div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <% }); %>
      </div>
      <div class="course-preview-list">
        <% coursePreview.filter(function(c) { return c.displayType === 'list'; }).forEach(function(c) { %>
        <a class="course-preview-list-item" href="<%= c.videoUrl %>">
          <span class="course-preview-list-num"><%= c.unit %></span>
          <span class="course-preview-list-title"><%= c.title %></span>
        </a>
        <% }); %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================== -->
  <!-- SECTION 6: INSTRUCTOR    -->
  <!-- ======================== -->
  <section class="instructor bg-cream fade-up" id="instructor">
    <div style="max-width:var(--max-width);margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="section-label">認識講師</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading">由真正實踐一人公司的人來教你</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="instructor-inner">
      <div class="instructor-photos">
        <img class="main-photo" src="https://raymondhouch.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/137-vertical-1472x2048.webp" alt="雷蒙——超級個體工作術講師">
        <div class="instructor-sub-photos">
          <div class="sub-placeholder">TEDx 演講</div>
          <div class="sub-placeholder">Podcast 訪談</div>
          <div class="sub-placeholder">知識春晚</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="instructor-name">侯智薰（雷蒙）</div>
        <div class="instructor-title-text">「雷蒙三十」創辦人 · 一人公司實踐者</div>
        <p class="instructor-bio">幫助忙碌的現代人聰明工作、好好生活。開創線上學習 3.0 模式的「Notion 線上訓練營」；為台灣線上課程「首例」—— 募資期過後 2 年內，長銷破萬人的課程產品。</p>
        <p class="instructor-bio">
          2017 年｜在外商 SaaS 全遠距、接案工作<br>
          2019-2021 年｜職場闘蕩期，拿下全部門第一績效<br>
          2021 年｜白手起家＆借貸 100 萬創業<br>
          2024 年｜年營收破 1,000 萬
        </p>
        <p class="instructor-bio">除了經營線上教學產品，寫電子報，也協助許多企業做數位轉型，導入 Notion 專案和工作管理系統。累積超過 500 場的演講，包含受邀至 TEDx 舞台，或到得到 APP 知識春晚面對萬人演講。</p>
        <p class="instructor-tagline">「把自己從職場新人到一人公司的驗證路徑，整理成你能直接用的方法。」</p>

        <div class="instructor-stats">
          <div class="instructor-stat">
            <div class="instructor-stat-num">1,000萬+</div>
            <div class="instructor-stat-label">年營收 (2024)</div>
          </div>
          <div class="instructor-stat">
            <div class="instructor-stat-num">10,000+</div>
            <div class="instructor-stat-label">課程學員</div>
          </div>
          <div class="instructor-stat">
            <div class="instructor-stat-num">500+</div>
            <div class="instructor-stat-label">場演講</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================== -->
  <!-- BOOK SECTION             -->
  <!-- ======================== -->
  <section class="book-section fade-up">
    <div class="book-layout">
      <div class="book-mockup">
        <div class="book-3d">
          <div class="book-cover">
            <div class="book-question">?</div>
          </div>
          <div class="book-bottom-pages"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="section-label" style="color:var(--orange);">即將出版</div>
        <div class="book-info-desc">
          我們正在將課程中最核心的方法論，濃縮成一本可以隨時翻閱的實體書。書中會收錄課程未公開的案例分析、工具模板，以及更多雷蒙親身實踐的心得。
        </div>

        <div class="book-previews">
          <div class="book-preview-img"><div class="book-preview-placeholder">書籍內頁 1</div></div>
          <div class="book-preview-img"><div class="book-preview-placeholder">書籍內頁 2</div></div>
          <div class="book-preview-img"><div class="book-preview-placeholder">書籍內頁 3</div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="book-form">
          <div class="book-form-label">新書上市時第一時間通知你</div>
          <!-- 替換為 Kit (ConvertKit) 嵌入表單 -->
          <div class="book-form-row">
            <input type="email" class="book-form-input" placeholder="輸入你的 Email">
            <button class="book-form-btn">訂閱通知</button>
          </div>
          <div class="book-form-note">我們不會發送垃圾郵件，僅在新書上市時通知你。</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================== -->
  <!-- SECTION 7: TESTIMONIALS  -->
  <!-- ======================== -->
  <section class="testimonials bg-yellow fade-up">
    <div style="max-width:var(--max-width);margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
      <h2 class="section-heading">各界好評</h2>
      <div class="divider" style="max-width:120px;margin:1rem auto 0;"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial-grid">
      <% testimonials.forEach(function(t) { %>
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-quote">「<%= t.quote %>」</div>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar"><% if (t.avatar) { %><img src="<%= t.avatar %>" alt="<%= t.author %>"><% } %></div>
          <div>
            <div class="testimonial-author-name"><%= t.author %></div>
            <div class="testimonial-author-role"><%= t.role %></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================== -->
  <!-- SECTION 8: MEETUP        -->
  <!-- ======================== -->
  <section class="meetup bg-cream fade-up">
    <div class="meetup-intro">
      <div class="section-label">超級個體小聚</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading">不只線上學習，更有實體交流</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <p class="meetup-desc">
        定期舉辦的「超級個體小聚」，讓學員們在實體空間裡交流、碰撞想法。在這裡，你會遇到和你一樣正在打造理想生活的夥伴——不同背景、不同產業，但同樣渴望掌控自己人生的現代人。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 小聚下拉選單 -->
    <div class="meetup-select-wrap">
      <select class="meetup-select" onchange="switchMeetup(this.value)">
        <% meetupPhotos.forEach(function(meetup, mi) { %>
        <option value="<%= mi %>"><%= meetup.label %></option>
        <% }); %>
      </select>
    </div>

    <% meetupPhotos.forEach(function(meetup, mi) { %>
    <div class="meetup-panel<%= mi === 0 ? ' active' : '' %>" data-meetup="<%= mi %>">
      <div class="meetup-gallery">
        <% meetup.photos.forEach(function(photo, pi) { %>
        <div class="meetup-thumb" onclick="openLightbox(<%= pi %>)"><img src="<%= photo %>" alt="超級個體小聚" loading="lazy"></div>
        <% }); %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <% }); %>
  </section>

  <!-- Lightbox -->
  <div class="lightbox-overlay" id="lightbox">
    <button class="lightbox-close" onclick="closeLightbox()">&times;</button>
    <button class="lightbox-nav lightbox-prev" onclick="navLightbox(-1)">&#8249;</button>
    <img class="lightbox-img" id="lightbox-img" src="" alt="小聚照片">
    <button class="lightbox-nav lightbox-next" onclick="navLightbox(1)">&#8250;</button>
    <div class="lightbox-counter" id="lightbox-counter"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============================== -->
  <!-- SECTION 9: STUDENT ARTICLES    -->
  <!-- ============================== -->
  <section class="student-articles bg-dark fade-up" id="student-articles">
    <div style="max-width:var(--max-width);margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="section-label">學員見證</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="color:var(--cream);">上過課的學員，這樣說</h2>
      <div class="divider-light"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="article-grid">
      <% studentArticles.forEach(function(a) { %>
      <a href="<%= a.link %>" target="_blank" class="article-card">
        <% if (a.image) { %>
        <img class="article-card-img" src="<%= a.image %>" alt="">
        <% } else { %>
        <div class="article-card-img-placeholder">文章封面圖</div>
        <% } %>
        <div class="article-card-body">
          <div class="article-card-tag"><%= a.tag %></div>
          <div class="article-card-title"><%= a.title %></div>
          <div class="article-card-excerpt"><%= a.excerpt %></div>
          <div class="article-card-meta"><%= a.meta %></div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <% }); %>
    </div>

    <!-- Threads 嵌入 -->
    <div class="threads-grid" id="threads-grid">
      <% threads.forEach(function(t) { %>
      <blockquote class="text-post-media" data-text-post-permalink="<%= t.permalink %>" data-text-post-version="0"></blockquote>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
    <script async src="https://www.threads.net/embed.js"></script>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================== -->
  <!-- SECTION 10: TALKS        -->
  <!-- ======================== -->
  <section class="bg-dark fade-up" style="padding:5rem 1.5rem;" id="talks">
    <div style="max-width:var(--max-width);margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="section-label">拆解 7+ 位高手的實戰經驗</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="color:var(--cream);">超級個體直播對談</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="talks-articles">
      <% talks.forEach(function(talk) { %>
      <a href="<%= talk.link %>" target="_blank" class="talks-article-card">
        <div class="talks-article-thumb"><img src="<%= talk.image %>" alt="<%= talk.alt %>"></div>
        <div class="talks-article-body sr-only">
          <div class="talks-article-title"><%= talk.title %></div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:2rem;">
      <a href="<%= ctaLinks.talkSignup.url %>" class="cta-orange"><%= ctaLinks.talkSignup.label %></a>
    </div>

<% if (internationalCases.length > 0) { %>
    <!-- 國外超級個體案例 -->
    <div style="max-width:var(--max-width);margin:4rem auto 1.25rem;">
      <div class="section-label">國外超級個體案例</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="color:var(--cream);">他們怎麼做到的？</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="talks-articles">
      <% internationalCases.forEach(function(c) { %>
      <a href="<%= c.link %>" target="_blank" class="talks-article-card">
        <div class="talks-article-thumb"><img src="<%= c.image %>" alt="<%= c.alt %>"></div>
        <div class="talks-article-body sr-only">
          <div class="talks-article-title"><%= c.title %></div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
<% } %>
  </section>

  <!-- ================================ -->
  <!-- MEDIA INTERVIEWS                 -->
  <!-- ================================ -->
  <section class="media-section bg-dark fade-up" id="media">
    <div style="max-width:var(--max-width);margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="section-label">媒體訪談</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="color:var(--cream);">從上班族到一人公司：雷蒙的真實故事</h2>
      <div class="media-intro">
        我在不同節目聊過關於「一人公司、內容創作、數位工具、以及怎麼跳出上班族的框架，活出自由的過程」。從創業初期的摸索，到打造品牌《雷蒙三十》的背後思考。<br><br>
        不管你是對職涯轉型、自由接案，或個人品牌感興趣，這些對話都能讓你看到，我是如何探索、學習、實踐「一人公司」的生活方式。
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="media-grid">
      <% media.forEach(function(m) { %>
      <a href="<%= m.link %>" target="_blank" class="media-card">
        <div class="media-card-thumb">
          <img src="<%= m.image %>" alt="">
          <% if (m.type === 'video') { %><div class="media-card-play"></div><% } %>
        </div>
        <div class="media-card-body">
          <div class="media-card-type media-card-type--<%= m.type %>"><%= m.type === 'video' ? '▶ 影片' : '✎ 文章' %></div>
          <div class="media-card-source"><%= m.source %></div>
          <div class="media-card-title"><%= m.title %></div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
  </section>

